name: Sublimetext3
body:
Cracked binaries for sublime text 3 build 3059. Installers and portable versions are included but can also be found at http://www.sublimetext.com/3.

64bit linux users may have to apt-get install ia32-libs to be able to run the 32bit crack.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
